snippet.title: March 2022 Alpha Gameplay Preview | Mines of Dalarnia
snippet.description:
March 2022 Mines of Dalarnia 2.0 Testnet Alpha Gameplay Preview

Join thousands of miners and start playing now.
Join our Discord community: https://discord.gg/minesofdalarnia

Mines of Dalarnia is a F2P, blockchain action-adventure platform-mining game where the player controls a character and guides them through a procedurally generated level (plot), mining through various earth blocks to discover and collect minerals of multiple rarities.

Website: https://www.minesofdalarnia.com
Blog: https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com
FAQ: https://www.minesofdalarnia.com/faqmod/index.html

Mines of Dalarnia March 2022 Recap: https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/mines-of-dalarnia-march-2022-recap-9f626cabaef6

Mines of Dalarnia: Backstory and Lore: https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/mines-of-dalarnia-backstory-and-lore-c4c7a06b94c3

Twitter: https://twitter.com/MinesOfDalarnia
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gaming/minesofdalarnia

Discord: https://discord.gg/minesofdalarnia
Telegram group: https://t.me/MinesOfDalarnia
Channel: https://t.me/minesofdalarnia_ann

Workinman Interactive: https://workinman.com
